---
description: Agent OS routing rule (thin shim)
globs:
  - "**/*"
alwaysApply: true
---

1) Read root `AGENTS.md` first.
2) Then read `docs/TASKS.md`.
3) Then read the assigned/active task file in `docs/tasks/`.
4) Read `docs/PRD.md` and `docs/workflows/*` only when needed.

If no active task exists: pick a `todo` item from `docs/TASKS.md`, or create a new task from `docs/tasks/TEMPLATE.md` and add it to the board before implementation.
